WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:00.800 align:middle line:90%


00:00:00.800 --> 00:00:03.730 align:middle line:90%
>> I had depression.

00:00:03.730 --> 00:00:06.332 align:middle line:84%
And the depression
led me to drinking.

00:00:06.332 --> 00:00:07.540 align:middle line:90%
I wasn't being a good father.

00:00:07.540 --> 00:00:08.797 align:middle line:90%
My dog was scared of me.

00:00:08.797 --> 00:00:09.880 align:middle line:90%
My kids were scared of me.

00:00:09.880 --> 00:00:12.610 align:middle line:10%
And now, things
are just changed.

00:00:12.610 --> 00:00:16.040 align:middle line:10%
It's like from darkness
to light, basically.

00:00:16.040 --> 00:00:17.694 align:middle line:90%
The San Pedro saved me.

00:00:17.694 --> 00:00:25.438 align:middle line:90%


00:00:25.438 --> 00:00:29.310 align:middle line:84%
So this is like a bit
of a secret location.

00:00:29.310 --> 00:00:30.300 align:middle line:90%
This is the place.

00:00:30.300 --> 00:00:33.310 align:middle line:84%
>> We shouldn't be filming
too many details here, huh?

00:00:33.310 --> 00:00:34.760 align:middle line:90%
We're off in Alacante.

00:00:34.760 --> 00:00:38.395 align:middle line:84%
And we're going to go
find some San Pedro.

00:00:38.395 --> 00:00:39.317 align:middle line:90%
>> Don't you see it?

00:00:39.317 --> 00:00:40.125 align:middle line:90%
>> Oh shit.

00:00:40.125 --> 00:00:41.005 align:middle line:90%
>> And there.

00:00:41.005 --> 00:00:42.604 align:middle line:90%
>> Wow.

00:00:42.604 --> 00:00:43.490 align:middle line:90%
[LAUGHS]

00:00:43.490 --> 00:00:44.650 align:middle line:90%
>> That's quite a bit, eh?

00:00:44.650 --> 00:00:47.590 align:middle line:90%


00:00:47.590 --> 00:00:48.600 align:middle line:90%
It's a bit of a jungle.

00:00:48.600 --> 00:00:50.085 align:middle line:90%
But, I mean, look at these.

00:00:50.085 --> 00:00:52.350 align:middle line:84%
These are, like,
beautiful specimens.

00:00:52.350 --> 00:00:54.190 align:middle line:84%
Look how thick and
juicy these are.

00:00:54.190 --> 00:00:55.860 align:middle line:90%
It's like being a beekeeper.

00:00:55.860 --> 00:00:57.660 align:middle line:84%
Getting stung is
part and parcel.

00:00:57.660 --> 00:00:59.230 align:middle line:84%
>> It's a rite of
passage, right?

00:00:59.230 --> 00:01:01.830 align:middle line:84%
>> Echinopsis peruviana
cactus, more commonly referred

00:01:01.830 --> 00:01:04.590 align:middle line:84%
