the psychedelic and healing

00:01:04.590 --> 00:01:06.120 align:middle line:90%
properties of mescaline.

00:01:06.120 --> 00:01:07.800 align:middle line:84%
The use of these
cacti in ceremonies

00:01:07.800 --> 00:01:09.840 align:middle line:84%
in South and Central
North America

00:01:09.840 --> 00:01:12.680 align:middle line:84%
can be tracked back
nearly 6,000 years.

00:01:12.680 --> 00:01:14.550 align:middle line:84%
Sanson has taken a
more casual approach,

00:01:14.550 --> 00:01:17.100 align:middle line:84%
preparing it for his friends
to go on a sacred nature walk.

00:01:17.100 --> 00:01:19.850 align:middle line:84%
>> I think there must
be about 20 kilos there.

00:01:19.850 --> 00:01:20.797 align:middle line:90%
>> It's so much.

00:01:20.797 --> 00:01:21.630 align:middle line:90%
>> It's a whole bag.

00:01:21.630 --> 00:01:25.466 align:middle line:84%
That'll be enough 12
people, let's say.

00:01:25.466 --> 00:01:28.200 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, after it's been
boiled for two or three hours,

00:01:28.200 --> 00:01:31.130 align:middle line:90%
