00:01:31.130 --> 00:01:32.030 align:middle line:90%
>> Cool.

00:01:32.030 --> 00:01:32.830 align:middle line:90%
Almost perfect.

00:01:32.830 --> 00:01:34.660 align:middle line:84%
>> So if you want
to strain it off.

00:01:34.660 --> 00:01:35.460 align:middle line:90%
>> Gorgeous.

00:01:35.460 --> 00:01:36.310 align:middle line:90%
>> And there we have it.

00:01:36.310 --> 00:01:37.190 align:middle line:90%
>> All right.

00:01:37.190 --> 00:01:38.560 align:middle line:90%
