00:01:38.560 --> 00:01:40.750 align:middle line:90%
>> It's mescaline soup.

00:01:40.750 --> 00:01:42.900 align:middle line:90%
>> Basically.

00:01:42.900 --> 00:01:44.390 align:middle line:90%
>> It doesn't smell bad at all.

00:01:44.390 --> 00:01:45.870 align:middle line:84%
It smells kind of
