00:01:45.870 --> 00:01:47.000 align:middle line:90%
>> How it goes.

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:49.285 align:middle line:84%
>> I don't think that
would taste good, though.

00:01:49.285 --> 00:01:54.130 align:middle line:84%
>> I mean, I'd really been
on sort of a downhill spiral.

00:01:54.130 --> 00:01:58.045 align:middle line:84%
Alcohol and depression were the
root causes of the unhappiness,

00:01:58.045 --> 00:01:58.870 align:middle line:90%
